{"word":"H3404 - יְרִיָּה - Yᵉrîyâh - yer-ee-yaw' - Jeriah","slug":"H3404","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יְרִיָּה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Yᵉrîyâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yer-ee-yaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Jeriah"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>יריּהוּ יריּה</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>yerı̂yâh yerı̂yâhû</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>yer-ee-yaw'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Jerijah or Jeriah = \"taught by Jehovah\" <ol><li>a Kohathite Levite and chief of the house of Hebron when David organised the service</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H3384\">H3384</a> and <a href=\"#/H3050\">H3050</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3138\">H3138</a>, <a href=\"#/H3139\">H3139</a>, <a href=\"#/H3140\">H3140</a>, <a href=\"#/H3384\">H3384</a>, <a href=\"#/H3385\">H3385</a>, <a href=\"#/H3400\">H3400</a>, <a href=\"#/H4175\">H4175</a>, <a href=\"#/H4176\">H4176</a>, <a href=\"#/H8451\">H8451</a>, <a href=\"#/H8452\">H8452</a>"}]}